- cs.SD (Software Development) is another possible category as the paper deals with the development and maintenance of software applications. 
- cs.MOB (Mobile Computing) is relevant as the paper specifically focuses on mobile applications and their platforms. 
- cs.SW (Software) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the quality improvement of software applications.
